# Repository Context — openwrt-packages-feed

> **Read `.github/AGENT_CONTEXT.md` for the full repository operation guide.**

## Critical Rules

1. This repo auto-syncs from upstream daily (UTC 03:00) via `sync.py` + GitHub Actions.
2. Files in `luci-app-*/` and `luci-theme-*/` directories are **synced content** — modifications will be overwritten, new files will be deleted.
3. Safe locations for custom content: `.github/`, `README.md`, `sync.py`, `sync.log`, `LICENSE`, `.gitignore`.
4. To add sync sources: edit `SOURCES` in `sync.py`.
5. To protect custom files from sync deletion: add top-level dir name to `protected` set in `sync.py`.
6. Sync uses Git blob SHA for incremental comparison — only changed files are downloaded.
7. Protected items: `.github`, `.git`, `.gitignore`, `sync.py`, `sync.log`, `README.md`, `LICENSE`.

